/ = render partial: "stolen_localized_police_checklist", locals: { stolen_record: @bike.current_stolen_record, police_report_present: police_report_present }
-# We only have recommendations for reporting your theft to police if your bike is reported stolen in the netherlands, country_code: NL
- netherlands = Country.find_by_iso("NL")
- if stolen_record.country_id == netherlands.id
  %li{ class: police_report_present ? "completed-item" : "" }
    %span.checklist-checkbox
      = "&#10003;".html_safe if police_report_present
      File a Police report

      A) Online (DigiD required) via this link: https://www.politie.nl/aangifte-of-melding-doen/voorbereiding-aangifte/diefstal-fiets.html
      Note: DigiD is a digital identification of people living in the NL. Kind of like the Global ID, only on a Dutch governmental level
      B) By a phone
      Simply call 0900-8844 (local tariff applies). You will usually get a phone call appointment for later, on which you give Police the information.
      C) On a police station
      Search for the closest police stations via this link: https://www.politie.nl/mijn-buurt/politiebureaus
  /   %span.checklist-text
  /     - bike_link = link_to(t(".a_police_report"), edit_bike_path(id: @bike.to_param, page: "theft_details"))
  /     = t(".add_bike_link_to_your_theft_report_html", bike_link: bike_link)
  /   %ul
  /     %li{ class: submitted_to_police_services ? "completed-item" : "" }
  /       %span.checklist-checkbox
  /         = "&#10003;".html_safe if submitted_to_police_services
  /       %span.checklist-text
  /         = t(".push_bike_info_to")
  /         = link_to t(".leads_online"), t(".leads_online_url")
  /         = t(".bike_index_does_this")
  /       - if serial_unknown
  /         %span.text-danger= t(".requires_a_serial_number")
  /     %li{ class: submitted_to_police_services ? "completed-item" : "" }
  /       %span.checklist-checkbox
  /         = "&#10003;".html_safe if submitted_to_police_services
  /       %span.checklist-text
  /         = t(".push_bike_info_to_law_enforcement")
  /         - if serial_unknown
  /           %span.text-danger= t(".requires_a_serial_number")
